         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><salute><pb facs="MS-SCHNITZLER-B-0008-B-00002-000-00121"/>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Wir wollen von <date>14</date><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><add place="below">Juli</add> an in <hi rend="underline" n="1"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb895">Strobl</rs></hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><hi rend="underline" n="1"><rs ref="#pmb51516" type="place">Hôtel a See</rs></hi> sein.</p><closer>Herzliche Grüsse Ihnen u. den Ihren.<lb/><signed>Richard</signed></closer></div>
